CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 7, 1961, pg. A29 reads: " "Golfer Of The Year" - Jerry Sumpter (left) is all smiles as he receives the "Golfer of the Year" trophy from Jack Wright, president of the Dandy Duffers. The trophy was presented to Sumpter during festivities at the Vogue Terrace recently. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Golfer Jerry Sumpter receiving Golfer of the Year award from Dandy Duffers president Jack Wright, posed in Vogue Terrace
